$ Relational Mechanics
by: → Wissenschaft/Geozentrik/Personen/Andre-Koch-Torres-Assis

{ Ptolemäisches und koopernikanische Anschauung

  "
    As we have seen, Leibniz and Mach emphasized that the Ptolemaic geocentric
    system and the Copernican heliocentric system are equally valid and correct.
  " [ S. 190 ]

  Vgl. Wissenschaft/Geozentrik/Personen/Robert-Sungenis[Sungenis], Galileo was Wrong, 7. Aufl, S.129 ff.

